        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2652",
        "content": "On the other hand, it is certain that from comparatively early in the seventeenth century there were to be found here and there women who smoked.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-high",
        "gender": "F",
        "pitch": "normal",
