        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2652",
        "content": "But what quite disgusted our visitor was \"that when one drinks the health of any person in company, the custom of the country does not permit you to drink more than half the cup, which is filled up and presented to him or her whose health you have drunk.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-fast_e-normal",
