        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2652",
        "content": "She said she had smoked it for twenty years, and \"it always makes me giddy!\" The writer, in august nineteen thirteen, saw a woman seated by the roadside in County Down, Ireland, calmly smoking a large briar pipe.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-normal_s-normal_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
