        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-2652",
        "content": "She asked Dickens if he had ever \"read such infernal trash\" as mrs Gore's; and exclaimed \"Oh God! what a sermon we had here, last Sunday.\" Dickens and his two daughters-\"who were decidedly in the way, as we agreed afterwards\"--dined by invitation with the mother and daughter.",
